      "writtenOn": "2020-02-05T14:55:30Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Curious why this threshold. Won\u0027t whatever we fall back to have to do some version of copying the points to the GPU? Or is this is a case where SW PR is better? If the latter, should it be a pointCount() vs bounds tradeoff?",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 89,
        "startChar": 4,
        "endLine": 89,
        "endChar": 35
      },
      "revId": "7db56cc3698369fb29909251546131f04f22d79d",
